msgctxt "2820_Rio"
msgid "Um, can I ask what your name is?"
msgstr "Mm, ¿puedo preguntar cuál es tu nombre?"

msgctxt "2832_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm Tanimura. Your name's Rio, right?"
msgstr "Tanimura. Te llamas Rio, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "2844_Rio"
msgid "Yes! It's nice to meet you."
msgstr "¡Sí! Que bueno conocerte."

msgctxt "2856_Rio"
msgid "What do you do for a living?"
msgstr "¿A qué te dedicas?"

msgctxt "2868_Tanimura"
msgid "I don't really want to say..."
msgstr "No quiero hablar de eso..."

msgctxt "2880_Rio"
msgid "Oh, I'm sorry if that was too personal."
msgstr "Oh, lo siento si eso fue algo muy personal."

msgctxt "2892_Tanimura"
msgid "No, no. I just don't like making a big deal out of it."
msgstr "No, no. Es solo que no me gusta hacer de eso algo importante."

msgctxt "2904_Rio"
msgid "Hehehe. Now I'm really curious."
msgstr "Je, je, je. Ahora tengo mucha curiosidad."

msgctxt "2916_Tanimura"
msgid "Heh, okay, fine. I'm a cop."
msgstr "Bueno, está bien. Soy policía."

msgctxt "2928_Rio"
msgid "Oh! There's nothing wrong with a policeman visiting a hostess club, is there?"
msgstr "¡Oh! No hay nada malo que un policía visite un club de hostess, ¿verdad?"

msgctxt "2940_Tanimura"
msgid "I wouldn't be here if I thought so."
msgstr "No estaría aquí si eso fuera así."

msgctxt "2952_Tanimura"
msgid "You wouldn't be half Japanese, would you?"
msgstr "¿No serás mitad japonesa, verdad?"

msgctxt "2964_Rio"
msgid "Yes, I am! You could tell just by looking at me?"
msgstr "¡Sí, lo soy! ¿Se dio cuenta solo mirándome?"

msgctxt "2976_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah. I usually notice that kind of thing."
msgstr "Sí, normalmente me doy cuenta de ese tipo de cosas."

msgctxt "2988_Rio"
msgid "In fact, I speak Portuguese pretty well!"
msgstr "¡De hecho, me defiendo bastante bien con el portugués!"

msgctxt "3000_Tanimura"
msgid "Oh yeah? I can speak Chinese and Korean."
msgstr "¿Oh, de verdad? Yo puedo hablar chino y coreano."

msgctxt "3012_Rio"
msgid "Wow! I guess you win!"
msgstr "¡Wow! ¡Supongo que ganaste!"

msgctxt "3024_Tanimura"
msgid "Hehehe."
msgstr "Je, je, je."

msgctxt "3036_Rio"
msgid "Being a policeman must be hard."
msgstr "Ser policía debe ser duro."

msgctxt "3048_Tanimura"
msgid "It can be, especially in this city. It seems like a new incident happens every day."
msgstr "Especialmente en esta ciudad. Parece que cada día pasa algo nuevo."

msgctxt "3060_Rio"
msgid "You know, I actually saw you when you were chasing somebody, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "Sabes, recuerdo haberte visto persiguiendo a alguien, Tanimura-san."

msgctxt "3072_Tanimura"
msgid "Really? That's kind of embarrassing."
msgstr "¿De verdad? Qué vergüenza."

msgctxt "3084_Rio"
msgid "Not at all! You're keeping us all safe. Thank you!"
msgstr "¡Para nada! Nos mantienes a todos seguros. Muchas gracias."

msgctxt "3096_Tanimura"
msgid "Thanks. It makes it worth it when I hear things like that."
msgstr "Gracias. Vale la pena al oír cosas como esa."

msgctxt "3108_Himeka"
msgid "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."
msgstr "The dialogue will end after one round if you've entered a club more than once. Please report when this message is displayed."

